<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246829 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-4.jpg" alt="a wooden sculpture of a gray terrier with very long snout fur" width="1920" height="1440" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-4.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-4-640x480.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-4-960x720.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-4-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-4-285x214.jpg 285w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246830 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-2.jpg" alt="a whimsical wooden sculpture of a pug with large, bulky muscles" width="1920" height="1440" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-2.jpg 1920w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-2-640x480.jpg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-2-960x720.jpg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-2-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-2-285x214.jpg 285w" sizes="(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px"></p>
