<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignnone wp-image-246823 size-full" src="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-9.jpeg" alt="a wooden sculpture of a brown French bulldog" width="1538" height="1433" srcset="https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-9.jpeg 1538w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-9-640x596.jpeg 640w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-9-960x894.jpeg 960w, https://www.thisiscolossal.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/misato-9-1536x1431.jpeg 1536w" sizes="(max-width: 1538px) 100vw, 1538px"></p>
